{"tid":465252,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人樣衰到連街市阿姐都改口叫你做先生?","createTime":"2017-11-11T10:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T06:35:21.000Z","uid":157510,"like":267,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"488e0fb7f49b916cd0d9bb42994a07e849b0f1b5","tid":465252,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"咁即係咩意思?<br />\n明明頭先幫個中坑阿叔落單個時都識講靚仔要乜<br />\n點解輪到我個時就叫先生要乜?<br />\n仲要唔係普通一句先生要乜<br />\n而係 [靚..err...先生要乜?]<br />\n自問樣貌不差，有中上<br />\n係身高差左少少，得168<br />\n整體黎講雖不及金城武<br />\n但靚仔依個稱呼我仍然係當之無愧<br />\n所以我最後單都無落到就嬲爆爆走左<br />\n<br />\n但你唔好諗住我就咁就算數<br />\n我頭先已經寫左封投訴信比個老闆<br />\n你話我西客都係咁話<br />\n希望你藉此明白到自己係幾咁有眼無珠<br />\n<br />\n先生要乜&hellip;&hellip;我要你連份工都無埋啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849f738d388b72007ec8e589b9945ff6feb56a95","tid":465252,"uid":38359,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"佢咪就係個老闆囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955e11adab00b012dd00787d70bdb83b2ea677c2","tid":465252,"uid":44243,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4437acc088e037331f86771bb17a7e393c7e74bf","tid":465252,"uid":137912,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"最尾個句笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a7730cc8d686197d35e4e8c69bdeab85a9c9d3","tid":465252,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbfa65fb5879f81e514b6f7eda4126f07cbccf2","tid":465252,"uid":24596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces